OL,6,FRyan Evans, who has worked with the
OL,7,FReuters news agency since 2022, was
OL,8,Fkilled by a Russian missile in its
OL,9,Fongoing war with Ukraine
OL,11,FA former British soldier from Wrexham,
OL,12,Fwho was working with the news agency
OL,13,FReuters to cover the war in Ukraine,
OL,14,Fhas been killed in a strike in the
OL,15,Fcity of Kramatorsk.
