OL,3,CFormer British soldier from Wrexham
OL,4,Ckilled in missile strike in Ukraine
OL,6,FRyan Evans, 38, was working as a
OL,7,Fsafety adviser and had been with
OL,8,FReuters since 2022. He was killed
OL,9,Fafter a missile struck the Hotel
OL,10,FSapphire where he was staying with
OL,11,Fcolleagues.
OL,13,FThe news organisation say two
OL,14,Fjournalists who were working for them
OL,15,Fwere being treated in hospital, with
OL,16,Fone of them being seriously injured.
OL,18,FIn a statement, Reuters have said: "We
OL,19,Fsend our deepest condolences and
OL,20,Fthoughts to Ryan's family and loved
OL,21,Fones.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
