OL,3,CFormer British soldier from Wrexham
OL,4,Ckilled in missile strike in Ukraine
OL,6,F"Ryan has helped so many of our
OL,7,Fjournalists cover events around the
OL,8,Fworld; we will miss him terribly.
OL,10,F"We are urgently seeking more
OL,11,Finformation about the attack,
OL,12,Fincluding by working with the
OL,13,Fauthorities in Kramatorsk, and we are
OL,14,Fsupporting our colleagues and their
OL,15,Ffamilies."
OL,17,FOn social media, Mr Evans' wife Anne
OL,18,FEvans paid tribute to her "gentle
OL,19,Fgiant."
