OL,3,CFormer British soldier from Wrexham
OL,4,Ckilled in missile strike in Ukraine
OL,6,F"As some of you may know already, Ryan
OL,7,Fsadly passed away on Saturday, 24th
OL,8,FAugust. I can't even begin to explain
OL,9,Fhow much that man meant to me, how
OL,10,Fmuch I adored him with every part of
OL,11,Fme.
OL,13,F"He was my best friend and my soul
OL,14,Fmate, my everything. We used to laugh
OL,15,Fand joke about how he came into my
OL,16,Flife as a Knight in battered armour,
OL,17,Fbecause let's face it, he was in shiny
OL,18,Farmour once, but he had been through
OL,19,Fmore battles then I can even count.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
