OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F465A1724791019
OL,3,CFormer British soldier from Wrexham
OL,4,Ckilled in missile strike in Ukraine
OL,6,F"He was such a gentle giant. If anyone
OL,7,Fneeded anything ever he was there, he
OL,8,Fwould always put others first and
OL,9,Fhimself second."
OL,11,FIn the post Mrs Evans said that Mr
OL,12,FEvans leave behind his 18 month old
OL,13,Fson, Logan and his three other
OL,14,Fchildren Tristan, Felicity and
OL,15,FHarrison.
OL,17,FMrs Evans added that "Ryan Don Evans,
OL,18,Fyou are the love of my life, my
OL,19,Feverything, and I will miss you and
OL,20,Flove you - ALWAYS."
