OL,6,FThe Foreign Secretary David Lammy has
OL,7,Falso offered his condolences to Mr
OL,8,FEvans's family and condemned the
OL,9,F"cowardly" tactics used by Vladimir
OL,10,FPutin's Russia against Ukraine.
OL,12,FMr Lammy also criticised a wave of
OL,13,FRussian strikes on Monday which
OL,14,Ftargeted infrastructure across Ukraine.
OL,16,F"The UK utterly condemns Russia's
OL,17,Fcowardly missile and drone attacks on
OL,18,Fcivilian infrastructure across Ukraine
OL,19,Ftoday," he said.
